title: Can i change my region in preseason 2017
body: Hello i wanna change from eune to euw but i cant there is only change name tag pls help

replies.body: Transfers are still down due to technical difficulties.  :(  Updates will be posted [here ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/rlu6awv4-transfer-service-update)in the meantime, hang tight!
